taining hospital hygiene according to highest standards.</p>\r\n<p>This section aims to help making varied selection of facilities for disinfection and professional cleaning in order to maximize their effective operational use.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<ul class=list3>\r\n<li>Disinfection of surfaces</li>\r\n<li>Disinfection of medical devices</li>\r\n<li>Disinfection of public catering places</li>\r\n<li>Sterilization and HLD of endoscopes</li>\r\n<li>Disinfection of biological and medical waste</li>\r\n<li>Hygiene of skin</li>\r\n<li>Professional cleaning</li>\r\n</ul>',1,8,0,1,1,1,1386590530,94,1488623793,0,0,0,1386590520,1,'',0,0,0,0,0,'modDocument','en',1,'catalog/healthcare.html',0,0,1,NULL),(344,'document','text/html','Beauty salons and SPA','','','beauty-and-spa','',1,0,0,342,1,'','<p>We endeavor to bring functional and consumer properties of each product to specific client needs, offering means that correspond to narrower areas of application, which includes barber shops, beauty salons and SPAs, manicure and pedicure salons. Usage of \"NPO Specsintez\" products prevents emergence and spread of socially significant diseases and upgrades the status of institution among clients.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<ul class=\"list3\">\r\n<li>Disinfection of surfaces</li>\r\n<li>Disinfection and sterilization of medical items</li>\r\n<li>Disinfection of medical waste</li>\r\n<li>Hygiene of skin</li>\r\n<li>Skin antiseptics</li>\r\n<li>Hand care</li>\r\n<li>Floors cleaning</li>\r\n<li>Cleaning of sanitary rooms, balnearies</li>\r\n<li>Glass surfaces cleaning</li>\r\n<li>Treatment of metal surfaces</li>\r\n<li>Removal of stains and graffiti</li>\r\n</ul>',1,8,1,1,1,1,1386590559,94,1488624416,0,0,0,1386590520,1,'',0,0,0,0,0,'modDocument','en',1,'catalog/beauty-and-spa.html',0,0,1,NULL),(345,'document','text/html','Food industry','','','food-processing-industry','',1,0,0,342,1,'','<p><span style=\"color: #3a3a3a;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, serif;\"><span><span lang=\"en-US\">Foo